Achievements.Name: Private
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 20 of your enemies.

Achievements.Name: Sergeant
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 50 of your enemies.

Achievements.Name: Lieutenant
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 100 of your enemies.

Achievements.Name: Captain
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 250 of your enemies.

Achievements.Name: Colonel
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 500 of your enemies.

Achievements.Name: General
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 750 of your enemies.

Achievements.Name: Pistoleer
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 100 of your enemies with your pistol.

Achievements.Name: Knife Master
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 75 of your enemies with your knife.

Achievements.Name: Melee Hero
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must kill 50 of your enemies in close combat.

Achievements.Name: War Survivor
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on the Easy (or higher) difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: War Veteran
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on the Normal (or higher) difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: War Hero
Achievements.Description: Complete the game on the Hard difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Journalist
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must find all secret photographs in the game.

Achievements.Name: Bookworm
Achievements.Description: To earn this award you must find all secret documents in the game.
